        "info": "This automated safety system monitors battery voltage and prevents overcharging.\n\n**Visual Status Guide:**\n- Automation node GREEN = protection running\n- Automation node RED = protection stopped\n- DMM shows current voltage reading\n- Threshold shows comparison result\n- ELL shows load state (ON/OFF)\n\n**Control Methods:**\n1. Click button on Automation node\n2. Send 'start'/'stop'/'toggle' to Automation input\n3. Use BenchMesh UI automation controls\n4. HTTP API: POST /benchmesh/automations/{id}/toggle",
